# 📊 Power BI Sales Dashboard

This repository contains a Power BI project that visualizes sample sales data using interactive charts, slicers, and KPIs.

## 🔧 Tools Used
- Microsoft Power BI Desktop
- Excel (as sample data source)

## 📁 Project Files
- `SalesDashboard.pbix` – Main Power BI report file
- `sales_data.xlsx` – Sample data used for the dashboard

## 📸 Dashboard Highlights
- Total Sales & Units KPIs
- Sales by Region (Bar Chart)
- Sales by Sales Rep (Column Chart)
- Product Sales Distribution (Pie Chart)
- Time-based Sales Trend (Line Chart)
- Interactive Slicers (Region, Date)

## 📥 How to Use
1. Download the `.pbix` file
2. Open it in Power BI Desktop
3. Explore the dashboard and interact with filters

